message.body: is there a party going on?
Not one that I'm ! Am at Firestone but trying to decide where next. Josh is out having fun with surfers. you having more fun tonight than last night?
I suppose so. Went out again tonight
This town is pretty dead though
I'm heading to trolley...I bloody hate trolley!
Our new German girl is pretty cool. Seems the house will be cool for the next couple of months. Have yours blown the fuse yet :)
yeah, I hear ya. I've never been a huge fan. Lo Ho is probably the best of the bunch
Ha, not even close
Lo ho? I've never even been to the best of the bad bunch. We go to rubbish rooneys.
yeah not a rooneys fan. Logan House
Is it bad that I'd rather be in bed with cocoa?
it's across the street
no
hell I work tomorrow at 7am
We took your advice and went to logans. Much better! 7 am ! No hookers tonight then.
no, they all left already. Glad you're enjoying Lo Ho
I'm being introduced to car bombs. Bleurgh guinness... You should get to sleep if you're going to survive 4 days of work in a row!
survive four days of work in a row? I plan on working every day I am here
You need to build your stamina is all I mean.
For work obviously not anything else ;)
hey, HEY! about the other night, I needed to get some sleep
Ha I obviously meant work. No issues in that department.
I'm just kidding with you
but yeah, it would be nice to not have to be up the next day
But the dosh will be nice.
You can come back and buy a boat and drink champagne every night like a pimp.
ah, but I meant it would be nice to not have to get up the next day when we sleep together. Sleeping in for the win!
